      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real-world testing, not sponsored comparisons</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What I Actually Tested</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>â€¢ Same prompt: "consulting business website"</li>
            <li>â€¢ Launch time measured from prompt to publish-ready</li>
            <li>â€¢ Content quality assessed for copy accuracy</li>
            <li>â€¢ Design quality compared side-by-side</li>
            <li>â€¢ CRM features tested with real leads</li>
            <li>â€¢ Value calculation: Mixo vs Durable with separate tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Real Results Measured</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <li>â€¢ Mixo: 47 sec generation, 5 min edits = 6 min total</li>
            <li>â€¢ Durable: 78 sec generation, 8 min edits = 10 min total</li>
            <li>â€¢ Durable CRM saved $50/month in tools</li>
            <li>â€¢ Mixo saved $72/year for website-only needs</li>
            <li>â€¢ Both sites generated quality copy</li>
            <li>â€¢ Design quality: Mixo slightly more modern</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

